<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0706b" n="0706b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b02"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b03"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b04"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b05"/><div1 type="xu"><mulu type="序" level="1" label="No. 1313-A 青州百問序"/><head>No. 1313-A
<lb ed="X" n="0706b06"/> 青州百問序</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b07"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b08"/><p id="pX67p0706b0801">夫禪分五派。本乎出自一源。教列三乘。大底終歸一
<lb ed="X" n="0706b09"/>法。利生接物。若洪鐘隨扣而騰聲。遇緣即宗。猶大鑑
<lb ed="X" n="0706b10"/>對形而現影。是以高低普應。妍醜齊分。須令入聖超
<lb ed="X" n="0706b11"/>凡。必使識心見性。恭惟
<lb ed="C X" n="0706b12"/>青州法祖大師提綱振領。鼎新曹洞之宗。運智興悲。
<lb ed="X" n="0706b13"/>彌&CB00832;兒孫之&CB14342;。</p><p id="pX67p0706b1307" place="inline">師一日厭居京邑。退隱山林。聚十方
<lb ed="X" n="0706b14"/>僧。束三條篾。每向室中勘驗。皆明格外良規。用一對
<lb ed="X" n="0706b15"/>無孔竅鉗鎚。出百隻沒意頭符券。三世諸佛未免再
<lb ed="X" n="0706b16"/>鑄同函鑰匙。六代祖師更須重經大冶鑪&CB02021;。言言有
<lb ed="X" n="0706b17"/>據。字字無&CB00980;。爍破瞎衲子眼睛。扭轉杜禪和鼻孔。偏
<lb ed="X" n="0706b18"/>圓互換。玉線金針不易穿。主伴交參。銀山鐵壁應難
<lb ed="X" n="0706b19"/>透。或奪或縱。或放或收。或立一塵。或隳大地。&CB02649;忽忽
<lb ed="X" n="0706b20"/>出自心上。皆一一置作問端。雖聞流布。未甚光揚。往
<lb ed="X" n="0706b21"/>往叢林不知名者。多矣。憧憧籌室透斯語者。鮮焉。既
<lb ed="X" n="0706b22"/>弗讓天衣．晦堂．圓通底蘊之奇可。盥手焚香再拜。薰
<lb ed="X" n="0706b23"/>毫而為之頌。噫。知我罪我。其惟此書乎。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0706b24"/><p id="pX67p0706b2401" rend="margin-left:11em">林泉野衲從倫序</p></div1>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0706c" n="0706c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c01"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c02"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c03"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c04"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c05"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="青州百問"/><head type="no">No. 1313</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead>青州百問</jhead></juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c07"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c08"/><byline type="other">中都大萬壽禪寺辯和尚問</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c09"/><byline type="other">唐慈雲十身禪寺覺和尚答</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c10"/><byline type="other">燕京報恩禪寺林泉老人頌</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c11"/><byline type="other">華亭生生道人梓</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0706c1201">問。聲前薦得。落在今時。句後承當。迷頭認影。作麼生
<lb ed="X" n="0706c13"/>是空劫<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>前自<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">己</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">已</rdg></app>。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0706c1310" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。半夜石人無影像。縱橫誰辨
<lb ed="X" n="0706c14"/>往來源。</p><p id="pX67p0706c1404" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。大地山河瑞像全。丙丁求火又重宣。紅
<lb ed="X" n="0706c15"/>鑪點雪非情謂。碧岫滄浪絕妙玄。緣木取魚終錯
<lb ed="X" n="0706c16"/>矣。刻舟求&CB00669;必徒然。驊騮一自窺鞭影。忍俊追風
<lb ed="X" n="0706c17"/>過九天。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0706c1801">問。&CB00980;空問萬象。萬象答&CB00980;空。且道甚麼人證據。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0706c1819" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0706c19"/>六耳不同謀。</p><p id="pX67p0706c1906" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。萬象&CB00980;空不惜眉。分明問答報君
<lb ed="X" n="0706c20"/>知。須彌俛首非全諾。還似&CB00565;山半肯時。參飽客。莫
<lb ed="X" n="0706c21"/>狐疑。休待文殊下一椎。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0706c22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0706c2201">問。暫時不在。如同死人。且道在甚麼處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0706c2216" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。東西南
<lb ed="X" n="0706c23"/>北。</p><p id="pX67p0706c2302" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。毫忽之差。紅塵汩沒。至理一言。奪胎換骨。
<lb ed="X" n="0706c24"/>知不知。休恍惚。夜來兔角逞神通。擊碎多年山鬼
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0707a" n="0707a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a01"/>窟。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707a0201">問。門堨X身易。身堨X門難。如何是身堨X門底人。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a03"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707a0301" rend="margin-left:1em">答。呂大后。</p><p id="pX67p0707a0305" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。覿面分明仔細看。風流禪客莫顢
<lb ed="X" n="0707a04"/>頇。箇中本自無難易。剛被時人立易難。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707a0501">問。從天降下則貧寒。從地湧出則富貴。既是從天降
<lb ed="X" n="0707a06"/>下。為甚麼&CB00230;貧寒。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707a0608" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。甲乙丙丁。</p><p id="pX67p0707a0613" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。貧富須知祇
<lb ed="X" n="0707a07"/>在人。乾坤那更有&CB00565;親。隨家豐儉元平等。獘服華
<lb ed="X" n="0707a08"/>房各任真。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707a0901">問。盡大地是箇解脫門。把手拽不入。且道過在師。過
<lb ed="X" n="0707a10"/>在學人。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707a1004" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。子承父業。</p><p id="pX67p0707a1009" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。推不出。拽不入。解脫門
<lb ed="X" n="0707a11"/>開無處立。師資過犯總彌天。悔也應知追不及。追
<lb ed="X" n="0707a12"/>不及。入水還曾&CB00560;不濕。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707a1301">問。山河大地無纖毫過患。猶是轉身句。且道轉了後
<lb ed="X" n="0707a14"/>如何。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707a1403" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。舌頭在口堙C</p><p id="pX67p0707a1409" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。拽尾靈龜。擬忘其&CB00528;。其
<lb ed="X" n="0707a15"/>&CB00528;弗忘。翻成勞役。萬丈懸崖撒手時。&CB00560;跟點地無
<lb ed="X" n="0707a16"/>移易。無移易。昨夜東風滿四維。曉來頓覺花狼藉。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707a1701">問。不見一法。猶是半提。作麼生是全提底道理。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707a1719" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0707a18"/>石馬驟千山。</p><p id="pX67p0707a1806" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">陝</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">陜</rdg></app>府鐵牛赤骨立。芒繩掣斷應難
<lb ed="X" n="0707a19"/>&CB00697;。崑崙山上震雷音。大似一聲春霹靂。水草之餘
<lb ed="X" n="0707a20"/>無所知。&CB00230;來江岸聽&CB00918;笛。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707a21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707a2101">問。靈山四十九年。未&CB00573;道著一字。少室九年面壁。行
<lb ed="X" n="0707a22"/>行分明。還信得及麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707a2209" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。文不加點。</p><p id="pX67p0707a2214" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。談而不談。
<lb ed="X" n="0707a23"/>聽而不聽。玉潔<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB00457;</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">水</rdg></app>清。星衡藻鏡。全諾兮辜負<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">己</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">已</rdg></app>靈。
<lb ed="X" n="0707a24"/>半肯兮埋沒先聖。明眼禪和仔細參。莫隨狂解招
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0707b" n="0707b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b01"/>三病。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707b0201">問。&CB02494;難陀龍王無耳善聽。且道是甚麼人為他說。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b03"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707b0301" rend="margin-left:1em">答。張三李四。</p><p id="pX67p0707b0306" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。舜若多神失&CB00230;口。&CB02494;難&CB00442;龍居其
<lb ed="X" n="0707b04"/>右。再三再四乞玄言。不免為渠垂隻手。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707b0501">問。以泥洗泥即不問。以水洗水時若何。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707b0516" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。黃河入
<lb ed="X" n="0707b06"/>海流。</p><p id="pX67p0707b0603" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。水洗水。法幢高建超前軌。可怜一片老婆
<lb ed="X" n="0707b07"/>心。漏泄玄關親切旨。祇這是活句。休同死句參。鷓
<lb ed="X" n="0707b08"/>鴣啼在深花堙C</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707b0901">問。喫飯忘其飢。力充忘其飽。作麼生是力充底人。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b10"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707b1001" rend="margin-left:1em">答。巨靈&CB01769;手無多子。分破華山千萬重。</p><p id="pX67p0707b1016" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。跛挈痿
<lb ed="X" n="0707b11"/>羸軟弱儂。&CB00642;身紅爛臥荊叢。眉棱擬舉如山重。我
<lb ed="X" n="0707b12"/>道斯人力最充。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707b1301">問。一透龍門雲外路。莫作黃河點額魚。未審龍門在
<lb ed="X" n="0707b14"/>甚麼處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707b1404" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。洪波浩渺。白浪滔天。</p><p id="pX67p0707b1413" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。目斷平林與
<lb ed="X" n="0707b15"/>翠岑。千巖萬壑曉雲深。雷驚三級桃花浪。葛杖陶
<lb ed="X" n="0707b16"/>梭俊不禁。高著眼。莫麤心。此回蹉過實難尋。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707b1701">問。打破大唐國。覓箇不會佛法底人不得。設使&CB00697;得。
<lb ed="X" n="0707b18"/>堪作何用。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707b1805" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。觀音妙智力。能救世間苦。</p><p id="pX67p0707b1816" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。量材
<lb ed="X" n="0707b19"/>受職。是得非得。迥出規模。高超繩墨。大唐國內尋
<lb ed="X" n="0707b20"/>將來。且教屋媔~&CB01229;食。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707b21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707b2101">問。三千大千界。無剎不現身。為甚麼十方遊歷&CB00642;。不
<lb ed="X" n="0707b22"/>見佛行蹤。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707b2205" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。此去西天十萬里。</p><p id="pX67p0707b2213" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。普眼當時&CB00697;
<lb ed="X" n="0707b23"/>普賢。目睛猶若隱雲&CB00195;。方知覿面相逢處。好本元
<lb ed="X" n="0707b24"/>來天下傳。</p></sp></dialog>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0707c" n="0707c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0707c01"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707c0101">問。二邊純莫立。中道不須安。且道甚麼處相見。得箇
<lb ed="X" n="0707c02"/>端的。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707c0203" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。鼻孔大頭垂。</p><p id="pX67p0707c0209" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。佛殿行廊兩夾間。不
<lb ed="X" n="0707c03"/>妨稽首拜師顏。德雲面目周沙界。莫訝別峰絕仰
<lb ed="X" n="0707c04"/>攀。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707c05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707c0501">問。有口讚不盡。無言心自明。是則裂破&CB00980;空。不是則
<lb ed="X" n="0707c06"/>鬼家活計。上人端的處。道將一句來。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707c0615" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。不道。不道。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0707c07"/><p id="pX67p0707c0701" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。鳧短&CB15112;長。松直棘曲。李白桃紅。山青水綠。與麼
<lb ed="X" n="0707c08"/>酬酢。千足萬足。禪房一枕黑甜餘。方信無由容寵
<lb ed="X" n="0707c09"/>辱。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707c10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707c1001">問。古人道。一切不為。佛也不作。未審作箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707c1019" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0707c11"/>闡提漢。</p><p id="pX67p0707c1104" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。古洞雲深下&CB00560;難。轉身獨步入長安。五
<lb ed="X" n="0707c12"/>湖四海皆曾到。八水三川<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>&CB00642;觀。有意氣時添意
<lb ed="X" n="0707c13"/>氣。得盤桓處且盤桓。聖情凡解俱截斷。蠅利蝸名
<lb ed="X" n="0707c14"/>總不干。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707c15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707c1501">問。迴途轉位。直須戴角披毛。喚作畜生。得麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707c1518" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。飢
<lb ed="X" n="0707c16"/>&CB00290;渴飲。</p><p id="pX67p0707c1604" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。兀兀無知水牯牛。優游終不混常流。拖
<lb ed="X" n="0707c17"/>犁拽杷閑終日。未審何時是徹頭。逼拶處。莫輕酬。
<lb ed="X" n="0707c18"/>溈山書字深深意。浩浩名聞四百州。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707c19"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707c1901">問。若見諸相非相。則見如來。汝一切時中甚麼處歸
<lb ed="X" n="0707c20"/>依。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707c2002" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。心不負人。</p><p id="pX67p0707c2007" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。眼中撥盡黃金屑。調御十身
<lb ed="X" n="0707c21"/>猶屈節。不識人嫌強露顏。那堪仰嶠還饒舌。橫按
<lb ed="X" n="0707c22"/>鏌&CB03456;。傷龜恕鱉。幾箇禪流。皮下有血。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0707c23"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0707c2301">問。維摩一默。未出化門。目擊道存。顢頇佛性。洒落一
<lb ed="X" n="0707c24"/>句作麼生道。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0707c2406" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。六六三十六。</p><p id="pX67p0707c2412" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。跳出離微語默
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0708a" n="0708a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a01"/>關。橫身物外任安閑。從他杓柄談長短。但看山尖
<lb ed="X" n="0708a02"/>月一彎。洒落句。本非慳。恐隨流水到人間。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a03"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708a0301">問。我是他非。他是我非。唯之與阿。相去幾何。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708a0318" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。海
<lb ed="X" n="0708a04"/>闊山遙。</p><p id="pX67p0708a0404" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。是非海埵w身。得失林中著&CB00560;。這般一
<lb ed="X" n="0708a05"/>等禪和。不妨有些作略。擬詢相去幾何。別日為渠
<lb ed="X" n="0708a06"/>斟酌。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a07"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708a0701">問。闍王殺父。圓悟無生。善星出家。為甚麼生陷地獄。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a08"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708a0801" rend="margin-left:1em">答。據&CB00001;結案。</p><p id="pX67p0708a0806" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。愛惡俱忘。聖凡截斷。地獄天堂。
<lb ed="X" n="0708a09"/>猶窺葦管。迷悟情塵不立時。自然心地常平坦。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708a1001">問。路逢達道人。不將語默對。且道如何見得淺和深。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a11"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708a1101" rend="margin-left:1em">答。賤避貴。少避老。</p><p id="pX67p0708a1108" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB00234;手相將過海東。淺深難
<lb ed="X" n="0708a12"/>昧把梢翁。鷓鴣聲堮蝒廕魽C誰&CB00283;靈雲繼祖風。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708a1301">問。作是思惟時。十方佛皆現。而今思惟也。佛在甚麼
<lb ed="X" n="0708a14"/>處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708a1402" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。頂上無螺髻。</p><p id="pX67p0708a1408" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB02852;目生華。迷頭認影。淨地
<lb ed="X" n="0708a15"/>撒沙。平田掘井。根境識三。不勞馳騁。妙相本自圓
<lb ed="X" n="0708a16"/>成。莫學胭脂塗癭。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708a1701">問。若人識得心。大地無寸土。即今山河大地是有是
<lb ed="X" n="0708a18"/>無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708a1802" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。江南塞北。</p><p id="pX67p0708a1807" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。有無俱坐斷。獨露一山河。人
<lb ed="X" n="0708a19"/>境元非二。心塵不隔多。但能高著眼。何用動干戈。
<lb ed="X" n="0708a20"/>擊碎疑團還罄快。莫教平地起風波。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708a2101">問。背覺合塵即不問。背塵合覺是若何。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708a2116" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。劈腹剜
<lb ed="X" n="0708a22"/>心。</p><p id="pX67p0708a2202" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。塵寰終日竟忙忙。那事元來總不妨。舉步儻
<lb ed="X" n="0708a23"/>能離向背。更無岐路泣亡羊。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708a24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708a2401">問。未達境唯心。起種種分別。達境唯心<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>。分別即不
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0708b" n="0708b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b01"/>生。過關底道將一句來。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708b0110" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。柳綠花紅。</p><p id="pX67p0708b0115" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。懵憧無
<lb ed="X" n="0708b02"/>知。總不記得。一鏃遼空。萬機頓息。文殊不二門。維
<lb ed="X" n="0708b03"/>摩酬一默。牢看向上關。照顧白拈賊。走&CB00642;江南并
<lb ed="X" n="0708b04"/>塞北。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708b0501">問。少林九年。垂一則語。直至如今。諸方詀舉。未審諸
<lb ed="X" n="0708b06"/>人作麼生舉。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708b0606" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。徒勞側耳。</p><p id="pX67p0708b0611" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。退步應須自決。莫
<lb ed="X" n="0708b07"/>便亡鋒結舌。若也莽鹵顢頇。虧殺神光立雪。別。別。
<lb ed="X" n="0708b08"/>勿謂達磨無法可說。自是闍黎弄巧成拙。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708b0901">問。不用揚眉瞬目。&CB00594;拂敲&CB00646;。勿涉離微。甚處相見。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b10"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708b1001" rend="margin-left:1em">答。氣急殺人。</p><p id="pX67p0708b1006" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。大地非寬。微塵非窄。覿面相呈。撞
<lb ed="X" n="0708b11"/>頭磕額。擬議不知。攔腮便摑。全提正令摠權衡。萬
<lb ed="X" n="0708b12"/>里清風&CB00038;地生。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708b1301">問。水鳥樹林皆悉念佛念法。且道案山與主山說箇
<lb ed="X" n="0708b14"/>甚麼法。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708b1404" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。諦聽。諦聽。</p><p id="pX67p0708b1409" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。切忌追求。徒勞採摭。
<lb ed="X" n="0708b15"/>竺法蘭&CB00442;。未&CB00573;翻譯。諦聽諦聽兮不辨金&CB00428;。如是
<lb ed="X" n="0708b16"/>如是兮難分玉石。越凡情。絕朕&CB00528;。十寸應知為一
<lb ed="X" n="0708b17"/>尺。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708b1801">問。四十九年無不盡。為甚麼末後拈花始道傳。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708b1819" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0708b19"/>怜兒不覺醜。</p><p id="pX67p0708b1906" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。瞿曇平昔忒多羅。鋪席開張不柰
<lb ed="X" n="0708b20"/>何。末後拈花折倒處。洎乎笑殺老頭&CB00442;。阿呵呵。會
<lb ed="X" n="0708b21"/>也麼。幾縷斷霞橫雪嶽。一&CB00424;殘月挂&CB00195;蘿。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708b2201">問。絲懸綠水。浮定有無之意。且道為人在甚麼處。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0708b23"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708b2301" rend="margin-left:1em">答。移舟諳水勢。</p><p id="pX67p0708b2307" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。微風信止浪痕平。短棹飄飄一
<lb ed="X" n="0708b24"/>葉輕。月&CB00424;雲餌沉寒水。釣得金鱗始稱情。參禪客。
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0708c" n="0708c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c01"/>參禪客。莫待龍門遭點額。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708c0201">問。雲從龍。風從虎。且道仰山拄杖從箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708c0218" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。一
<lb ed="X" n="0708c03"/>棒一條痕。</p><p id="pX67p0708c0305" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。雲從龍。風從虎。仰山柱杖從雷雨。佛
<lb ed="X" n="0708c04"/>祖瞻之喪膽魂。德山見也忘區宇。杜禪和。休莽鹵。
<lb ed="X" n="0708c05"/>若非收得返魂香。爭<note n="0708001" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">散疑敢</note>散來撾塗毒&CB00655;。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708c0601">問。直得不恁麼來者。猶是兒孫事。如何是向上人。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c07"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708c0701" rend="margin-left:1em">答。半夜烏&CB00470;雪堻琚C</p><p id="pX67p0708c0709" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。瑞靄祥煙起鳳城。玉樓金
<lb ed="X" n="0708c08"/>殿月華明。祇聞闔國傳皇化。到了終須不得名。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708c0901">問。情生智隔從來事。息念忘緣又落空。如何得相應
<lb ed="X" n="0708c10"/>去。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708c1002" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。珍重。</p><p id="pX67p0708c1005" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。擊碎疑團便好休。何須又被有無
<lb ed="X" n="0708c11"/>收。欲令於是明真意。雲自高飛水自流。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708c1201">問。牛頭橫說&CB00594;說。不知有向上關捩子。如何是向上
<lb ed="X" n="0708c13"/>關捩子。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708c1304" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。踏著便轉。</p><p id="pX67p0708c1309" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。一撥靈機活鱍鱍。三賢
<lb ed="X" n="0708c14"/>十聖應難奪。箇中關捩少人知。不必尋行緣本末。
<lb ed="X" n="0708c15"/>大用神通變化時。虎頭虎尾同時捋。莫啾啾。休聒
<lb ed="X" n="0708c16"/>聒。德山棒兮臨濟喝。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708c1701">問。行玄體妙。落在今時。究理窮源。關山萬里。祇如未
<lb ed="X" n="0708c18"/>知有底人如何趣向。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708c1809" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。&CB00646;窄先臥。</p><p id="pX67p0708c1814" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。瘖&CB00484;盲聾。
<lb ed="X" n="0708c19"/>&CB00565;狂愚魯。百無所能。一無可取。是人多幸得如斯。
<lb ed="X" n="0708c20"/>鼠糞休將投。</p><p id="pX67p0708c2006" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">鼎釜。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708c2101">問。菩薩護生。猶戒草木。為甚麼南泉一刀兩段。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0708c2119" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0708c22"/>不妨疑著。</p><p id="pX67p0708c2205" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。斬&CB00339;芟蛇。大人境界。不解玄微。翻為
<lb ed="X" n="0708c23"/>&CB02852;怪。拍盲禪客細參詳。妙用縱橫看變態。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0708c24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0708c2401">問。念念釋迦出世。步步彌勒下生。為甚麼擬心即錯。
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0709a" n="0709a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a01"/>動念即乖。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709a0105" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。自倒自起。</p><p id="pX67p0709a0110" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。現在釋迦。未來彌勒。
<lb ed="X" n="0709a02"/>今古琣s。何&CB00573;隱匿。擬心動念轉迂迴。為報禪流
<lb ed="X" n="0709a03"/>休費力。出是非。超語默。人間幾箇知恩德。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a04"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709a0401">問。未離兜率。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>降王宮。未出母胎。度人<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>畢是如何。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a05"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709a0501" rend="margin-left:1em">答。枉費草鞋錢。</p><p id="pX67p0709a0507" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。耆闍山埵捔ˇ銵C不惜眉毛
<lb ed="X" n="0709a06"/>為指南。未出未離俱鈍滯。垛根禪客切須參。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a07"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709a0701">問。龍吟霧起。虎嘯風生。且道是甚麼人分上事。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709a0719" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0709a08"/>玄沙元是謝三郎。</p><p id="pX67p0709a0808" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。虎嘯龍吟。風清霧黑。不辨東
<lb ed="X" n="0709a09"/>西。難分南北。大悲千手運神通。擘破面門猶不識。
<lb ed="X" n="0709a10"/>何不識。黯黯乾坤如潑墨。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709a1101">問。指南一路。智者知&CB00565;。瑞草無根。為甚麼賢者不貴。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a12"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709a1201" rend="margin-left:1em">答。好事不如無。</p><p id="pX67p0709a1207" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。不貴知&CB00565;。俊哉奇偉。具眼
<lb ed="X" n="0709a13"/>阿師。人間幾幾。掣開金&CB02083;碎玄關。騎虎頭兮捋虎
<lb ed="X" n="0709a14"/>尾。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709a1501">問。三十年前尋&CB00669;客。為甚麼一見桃花更不疑。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709a1519" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0709a16"/>眼在面門前。</p><p id="pX67p0709a1606" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>悟桃花樂有餘。玄沙未保意何
<lb ed="X" n="0709a17"/>如。靈苗瑞草從滋茂。野父終須不肯鋤。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709a1801">問。鐘鳴鼓響。無非觀音入理之門。&CB00177;短松長。盡是毗
<lb ed="X" n="0709a19"/>盧一真境界。且如德山．臨濟是甚麼家風。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709a1917" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。兩&CB00560;
<lb ed="X" n="0709a20"/>踏地。</p><p id="pX67p0709a2003" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。咄。棒頭突出。&CB00287;○霄鶻。天眼龍睛不可窺。
<lb ed="X" n="0709a21"/>轉身返入蒼龍窟。雄雄七事用無窮。大辨從來還
<lb ed="X" n="0709a22"/>若訥。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709a23"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709a2301">問。依經解義。數比河沙。續焰聯芳。稻麻竹葦。祇如佛
<lb ed="X" n="0709a24"/>祖未生前。還有佛法也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709a2411" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。洎合恁麼去。</p><p id="pX67p0709a2417" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。佛
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0709b" n="0709b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0709b01"/>法有。釋迦老子徒開口。佛法無。達<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">磨</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">麼</rdg></app>尊者漫勞軀。
<lb ed="X" n="0709b02"/>五湖雲水休狂解。粥罷應須洗&CB00425;盂。逆耳忠言如
<lb ed="X" n="0709b03"/>不信。鐵圍山堸搕摰瞴C</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709b04"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709b0401">問。動容揚古路。不墮悄然機。且道那箇有分。那箇無
<lb ed="X" n="0709b05"/>分。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709b0502" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。有功者賞。</p><p id="pX67p0709b0507" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。片雲為雨下山頭。潤濕群萌
<lb ed="X" n="0709b06"/>&CB00642;九州。一&CB01356;齊平無向背。榮枯何用苦搜求。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709b07"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709b0701">問。迷時千卷少。悟後一言多。且道悟了底人。如何履
<lb ed="X" n="0709b08"/>踐。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709b0802" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。行不出戶。坐不當堂。</p><p id="pX67p0709b0811" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。迷悟端如眼媢苤C
<lb ed="X" n="0709b09"/>衲僧一見便傷神。要知履踐明白處。社飲村歌樂
<lb ed="X" n="0709b10"/>本真。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709b11"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709b1101">問。諸行無常。是生滅法。生滅滅<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>。寂滅為樂。恁麼會
<lb ed="X" n="0709b12"/>得。還徹也未。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709b1206" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。此義文長。</p><p id="pX67p0709b1211" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。徹與不徹。總未勦
<lb ed="X" n="0709b13"/>絕。曲為今時。證龜作鱉。踏&CB00642;叢林問&CB00642;人。了然無
<lb ed="X" n="0709b14"/>地容生滅。生滅求兮畢竟無。可怜特地捨全軀。得
<lb ed="X" n="0709b15"/>聞半偈雖忘楚。爭免人言不丈夫。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709b16"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709b1601">問。古人講得天花墜。石點頭。因甚重來訪祖師。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709b1619" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0709b17"/>碧眼胡僧笑點頭。</p><p id="pX67p0709b1708" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。事窮理變計多端。&CB00562;鈔焚燒
<lb ed="X" n="0709b18"/>許德山。一見龍潭成正覺。不妨袖手伴雲閑。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709b19"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709b1901">問。山河無隔礙。圓明離識情。如何領會。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709b1916" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。圓同太
<lb ed="X" n="0709b20"/>&CB00980;。無欠無餘。</p><p id="pX67p0709b2006" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。識情隔礙兩無端。領會應知下口
<lb ed="X" n="0709b21"/>難。般若談空空不有。常啼何必賣心肝。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709b22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709b2201">問。城東老母與佛同生。而不欲見佛。且道這婆子還
<lb ed="X" n="0709b23"/>有長處也無。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709b2306" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。夜深方見把針人。</p><p id="pX67p0709b2314" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。公案渾成
<lb ed="X" n="0709b24"/>見也麼。擬詢長短。不知他衲僧鼻孔人難摸。獨許
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0709c" n="0709c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0709c01"/>城東強老婆。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709c02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709c0201">問。世尊臨般涅槃時。曼殊大士請佛再轉法輪。世尊
<lb ed="X" n="0709c03"/>咄云。吾四十九年未&CB00573;道著一字。且如三乘十二分
<lb ed="X" n="0709c04"/>教自何而得。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709c0406" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。如是我聞。</p><p id="pX67p0709c0411" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。靈鷲祖翁。拘尸羅
<lb ed="X" n="0709c05"/>滅。原始要終。無法可說。五教三乘謾度量。龍宮海
<lb ed="X" n="0709c06"/>藏空羅列。空羅列兮因何得。千眼大悲也不識。休
<lb ed="X" n="0709c07"/>不識。憨皮袋是真彌勒。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709c08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709c0801">問。富樓那問佛。清淨本然。云何忽生山河大地。莫道
<lb ed="X" n="0709c09"/>富樓那。且如瞿曇還知痛痒麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709c0913" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。將此身心奉塵
<lb ed="X" n="0709c10"/>剎。是則名為報佛恩。</p><p id="pX67p0709c1009" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。山河大地元清淨。猶向
<lb ed="X" n="0709c11"/>瞿曇求畢竟。多少玄關僻執人。紅塵堆堸g真
<lb ed="X" n="0709c12"/>性。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709c13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709c1301">問。善財童子至妙高峰。七日&CB00697;德雲比丘不得。後別
<lb ed="X" n="0709c14"/>峰相見。且道是德雲否。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709c1410" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。相識滿天下。知心有幾
<lb ed="X" n="0709c15"/>人。</p><p id="pX67p0709c1502" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。是不是。妙高&CB00123;頂難行履。具眼禪人仔細參。
<lb ed="X" n="0709c16"/>正偏兼到非離此。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709c17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709c1701">問。岸如欲止先停棹。車若不行須打牛。如今打牛也。
<lb ed="X" n="0709c18"/>車行也未。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709c1805" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。下載清風付與誰。</p><p id="pX67p0709c1813" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。好箇溈山水
<lb ed="X" n="0709c19"/>牯牛。群靈般運了無休。方知羊鹿閑家具。古佛場
<lb ed="X" n="0709c20"/>中不肯收。行也未。為君酬。過後如何曾借問。他云
<lb ed="X" n="0709c21"/>平地兩條溝。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0709c22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0709c2201">問。了了常知故。言之不可及。為甚麼洪音震地。聵者
<lb ed="X" n="0709c23"/>不聞。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0709c2303" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。穿過髑髏。</p><p id="pX67p0709c2308" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。箇中若會不聞聞。曉了觀
<lb ed="X" n="0709c24"/>音第一門。眼睫眉毛俱解聽。何勞洪韻震乾坤。</p></sp></dialog>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0710a" n="0710a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a01"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710a0101">問。釣盡江波。金鱗始遇。且道甚麼處相見。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710a0117" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。負命
<lb ed="X" n="0710a02"/>者上&CB00424;。</p><p id="pX67p0710a0204" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。離&CB00230;磻溪與華亭。不從&CB00424;線得長鯨。煙
<lb ed="X" n="0710a03"/>波萬頃乘清興。肯學空舟載月明。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a04"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710a0401">問。為一大事因緣故。出現於世。如何是一大因緣。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a05"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710a0501" rend="margin-left:1em">答。止止不須說。</p><p id="pX67p0710a0507" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。大事因緣。群心仰慕。東土西天。
<lb ed="X" n="0710a06"/>徒勞指注。玉兔懷胎兮深隱紫微。崑崙舉步兮高
<lb ed="X" n="0710a07"/>超雲露。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710a0801">問。二祖禮拜了。依位而立。初祖云。汝得吾髓。且道祖
<lb ed="X" n="0710a09"/>師還道盡也未。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710a0907" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。&CB00230;請和尚道。</p><p id="pX67p0710a0913" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。三拜畢。依位
<lb ed="X" n="0710a10"/>立。便云得髓令承襲。兩桂芬芳直至今。五花爛熳
<lb ed="X" n="0710a11"/>盈都邑。端的處。未為難。盡不盡兮君自看。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710a1201">問。夜半正明。天曉不露。為甚麼道黑白未分前猶是
<lb ed="X" n="0710a13"/>正中偏。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710a1304" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。石女畫娥眉。</p><p id="pX67p0710a1310" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。空劫威音外。壺天不
<lb ed="X" n="0710a14"/>夜時。嶺頭雲吐月。海內島銜曦。半暗半明唯半露。
<lb ed="X" n="0710a15"/>無私照燭不萌枝。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a16"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710a1601">問。不披毛。不戴角。異類迴途事若何。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710a1615" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。十字街頭。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a17"/><p id="pX67p0710a1701" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。露地白牛角不全。轉身獨步下層巔。饑&CB00290;渴飲
<lb ed="X" n="0710a18"/>無餘事。月一風前骨侖眠。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a19"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710a1901">問。一言道斷處。千古意分明。為甚麼高峰頂上有一
<lb ed="X" n="0710a20"/>人不肯在。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710a2005" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。長安雖樂。</p><p id="pX67p0710a2010" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。千古雖非在一言。斯
<lb ed="X" n="0710a21"/>人不肯更無端。高峰頂上猶閑管。足見居塵量不
<lb ed="X" n="0710a22"/>寬。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710a23"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710a2301">問。白鷺下田千點雪。黃鶯上樹一枝花。且道是境不
<lb ed="X" n="0710a24"/>是。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710a2402" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。鳥銜花落碧巖前。</p><p id="pX67p0710a2410" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。不貴語親。秪圖眼正。
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0710b" n="0710b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0710b01"/>妍醜高低。難謾寶鏡。法燈擬議<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>輸機。今日禪流
<lb ed="X" n="0710b02"/>看性命。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710b03"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710b0301">問。寒山逢拾得。拍手笑呵呵。未審笑箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710b0318" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。飢
<lb ed="X" n="0710b04"/>嗔飽喜。</p><p id="pX67p0710b0404" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。寒山拾得笑呵呵。目擊心存會也麼。此
<lb ed="X" n="0710b05"/>意分明非委曲。更休特地覓&CB05070;訛。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710b06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710b0601">問。賓中辨主即不問。主中之主事何如。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710b0616" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。觀音頂
<lb ed="X" n="0710b07"/>上彌陀佛。</p><p id="pX67p0710b0705" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。主中主。玉宇天顏棲紫府。丹墀月浸
<lb ed="X" n="0710b08"/>影沉沉。彩雲無限遮廊廡。信不通。音亦絕。底事分
<lb ed="X" n="0710b09"/>明誰敢說。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710b10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710b1001">問。唯此一事實。餘二即非真。如何是真實底事。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710b1019" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。踏
<lb ed="X" n="0710b11"/>著秤鎚硬似鐵。</p><p id="pX67p0710b1107" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。三&CB00560;蜘蛛飛上天。&CB00642;參先聖與
<lb ed="X" n="0710b12"/>先賢。忽然撞著須彌柱。倒跨崑崙駕鐵船。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710b13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710b1301">問。達磨逢梁武。摩騰遇漢明。是則不隔纖毫。不是則
<lb ed="X" n="0710b14"/>兩重公案。上人參學眼在甚麼處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710b1414" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。日堿搕s。</p><p id="pX67p0710b1419" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0710b15"/>宗教分梁漢。佳聲震玉京。是非從此出。得失自茲
<lb ed="X" n="0710b16"/>生。雨過山添翠。雲開目倍明。空花元不有。何必怪
<lb ed="X" n="0710b17"/>雙睛。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710b18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710b1801">問。猿抱子歸青嶂後。鳥銜花落碧巖前。且道是甚麼
<lb ed="X" n="0710b19"/>人語。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710b1903" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。言不該典。非君子之所談。</p><p id="pX67p0710b1914" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。至理一言。
<lb ed="X" n="0710b20"/>不勞分棟。輸他夾山。疑殺法眼。錯商量。有何眼。莫
<lb ed="X" n="0710b21"/>學徐六空擔板。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710b22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710b2201">問。研窮至理。以悟為則。為甚麼祖師道不怕迷。祇怕
<lb ed="X" n="0710b23"/>悟。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710b2302" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。跣足履春&CB00457;。</p><p id="pX67p0710b2308" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。迷也何憂。悟也何怕。水月
<lb ed="X" n="0710b24"/>空花。從他變化。吹毛照雪倚天寒。殺活權衡獨柄
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0710c" n="0710c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c01"/>霸。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710c0201">問。有語不得道。無言鬼也嗔。且道意旨如何。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710c0218" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。舌
<lb ed="X" n="0710c03"/>頭無骨。</p><p id="pX67p0710c0304" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。巖松庭檜影蕭條。&CB00054;月玄猿恨未消。清
<lb ed="X" n="0710c04"/>韻連霄酬谷響。癡心猶自笑鷦鷯。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710c0501">問。有佛處不得住。無佛處急走過。且道衲僧家甚麼
<lb ed="X" n="0710c06"/>處安身立命。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710c0606" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。緊俏草鞋。</p><p id="pX67p0710c0611" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。瘦筇挑月入紅塵。
<lb ed="X" n="0710c07"/>不必擇居卜立身。有佛處同無佛處。趙州何用苦
<lb ed="X" n="0710c08"/>勞神。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c09"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710c0901">問。祖師道。見處不從眼見。聞處不從耳聞。靈雲．香嚴
<lb ed="X" n="0710c10"/>正眼在甚麼處。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710c1007" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。眉毛下。</p><p id="pX67p0710c1011" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。聞似不聞。見如不
<lb ed="X" n="0710c11"/>見。木竹桃花。乾坤普&CB00642;。心中雙眼頓圓明。六一俱
<lb ed="X" n="0710c12"/>亡無不見。閃電光中仔細時。何勞耳目生疲倦。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710c1301">問。斷絃續不得。為甚麼千古響泠泠。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710c1315" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。罕遇知音。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c14"/><p id="pX67p0710c1401" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。我道知音一箇無。知音縱有待何如。乾闥婆奏
<lb ed="X" n="0710c15"/>頭陀舞。習氣元來果未除。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c16"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710c1601">問。圓明了知。不因心念。未審從甚麼處念。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710c1617" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。分明
<lb ed="X" n="0710c17"/>記取。</p><p id="pX67p0710c1703" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。覺照圓明絕念時。更無一物可堪為。四臣
<lb ed="X" n="0710c18"/>喝退忘依所。雲倚西山月落遲。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c19"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710c1901">問。雖得六銷。猶未忘一。忘一之後。功歸何所。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710c1918" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。冬
<lb ed="X" n="0710c20"/>去寒食一百五。</p><p id="pX67p0710c2007" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。荒陂獵犬&CB01904;羚羊。蹤跡無餘得
<lb ed="X" n="0710c21"/>校量。畢竟元勳成底事。茙葵傾側奉朝陽。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0710c22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0710c2201">問。色見聲求俱是妄。問君那箇是如來。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0710c2216" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。明眼人
<lb ed="X" n="0710c23"/>難謾。</p><p id="pX67p0710c2303" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。乾屎橛。雲門指出靈山月。一道光含四百
<lb ed="X" n="0710c24"/>州。癡兒何必重相謁。色見聲求不契時。達磨半夜
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0711a" n="0711a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0711a01"/>辭梁闕。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711a02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711a0201">問。悟則言言般若。迷時句句瘡疣。為甚麼祖師道。悟
<lb ed="X" n="0711a03"/>之一字直須吐&CB00230;。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711a0308" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。心空及第歸。</p><p id="pX67p0711a0314" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。吐不出。嚥
<lb ed="X" n="0711a04"/>不入。迷悟情懷誰敢立。智炬煌煌照大千。白毫光
<lb ed="X" n="0711a05"/>媯普弁禳C</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711a06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711a0601">問。情忘識盡歸真諦。為甚麼絕點純清階下人。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711a0619" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。
<lb ed="X" n="0711a07"/>祇見錐頭利。</p><p id="pX67p0711a0706" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。白珪無玷。不足為貴。圓珠不穴。何
<lb ed="X" n="0711a08"/>可言純。相如有智兮還成鈍滯。罔象無心兮孰為
<lb ed="X" n="0711a09"/>因循。豈知李杜蘇黃輩。花酒叢中飽看春。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711a10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711a1001">問。自心起信。還信自心。且道信後如何行履。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711a1018" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。運
<lb ed="X" n="0711a11"/>水般柴。</p><p id="pX67p0711a1104" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。河堨Ⅶ河嵎隉C不須更買孫賓卜。忽
<lb ed="X" n="0711a12"/>然獲得便流通。頃刻&CB00642;達諸耳目。耳目達。無阻隔。
<lb ed="X" n="0711a13"/>縱橫妙用&CB01801;商客。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711a14"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711a1401">問。坐脫立亡猶未徹。石霜消息事如何。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711a1416" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。蒼天。蒼
<lb ed="X" n="0711a15"/>天。</p><p id="pX67p0711a1502" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。枯木花開。冷&CB01926;豆&CB15090;。石霜一宗。幾乎寂寞。侍
<lb ed="X" n="0711a16"/>者忒慣叢林。首座未&CB00573;行&CB00560;。東風忽&CB00380;&CB00642;坤維。點
<lb ed="X" n="0711a17"/>檢人間錯不錯。遍地桃花紅灼灼。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711a18"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711a1801">問。祖師道。知有底人。直須向異類中行。祇如不知有
<lb ed="X" n="0711a19"/>底人。向甚麼處行履。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711a1909" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。花襯馬蹄香。</p><p id="pX67p0711a1915" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。忽憶南
<lb ed="X" n="0711a20"/>泉水牯牛。溪頭溪尾自優游。牧童睡穩芒繩斷。明
<lb ed="X" n="0711a21"/>月孤圓萬里秋。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711a22"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711a2201">問。古人道。若論此事。直須似鏡常明。為甚麼道打破
<lb ed="X" n="0711a23"/>鏡來與汝相見。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711a2307" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。醜婦揚眉。</p><p id="pX67p0711a2312" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。成壞根源不可
<lb ed="X" n="0711a24"/>疑。休從照膽定良規。本來面目常相見。何用區區
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0711b" n="0711b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b01"/>手撥眉。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b02"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711b0201">問。離心意識參。出凡聖路學。祇如到這堙C參見阿誰。
<lb ed="X" n="0711b03"/>學箇甚麼。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711b0305" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。相識還如不相識。</p><p id="pX67p0711b0313" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。飢時喫飯。寒
<lb ed="X" n="0711b04"/>時著衣。無法可說。無師可依。震威一喝聾三日。&CB05232;
<lb ed="X" n="0711b05"/>瞎雙睛息萬機。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b06"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711b0601">問。不落因果。墮野狐身。不昧因果。脫野狐身。且道落
<lb ed="X" n="0711b07"/>昧二字是同是別。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711b0708" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。春蘭秋菊。</p><p id="pX67p0711b0713" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。通身&CB00642;身。何
<lb ed="X" n="0711b08"/>必不必。具眼阿師。試分得失。雷同兮採花成蜜。無
<lb ed="X" n="0711b09"/>別兮割汁為漆。實實雨過。寒蟬鳴唧唧。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b10"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711b1001">問。絕後重甦。方始欺君不得。作麼生是重甦底人。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b11"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711b1101" rend="margin-left:1em">答。作麼。作麼。</p><p id="pX67p0711b1106" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。名遂功成撒手行。迴途復妙幾人
<lb ed="X" n="0711b12"/>能。退身三步參詳去。不會休爭鬼眼精。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b13"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711b1301">問。脫&CB00230;籠頭卸角&CB00501;底人。向甚麼處安排。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711b1317" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。可上
<lb ed="X" n="0711b14"/>可下。</p><p id="pX67p0711b1403" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。明&CB00275;<note n="0711001" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">靜疑淨</note>靜几。莫厭蕭&CB00520;。籠頭角&CB00501;。不索驅除。
<lb ed="X" n="0711b15"/>妥妥帖帖。無欠無餘。橫眠側臥。一任卷舒。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b16"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711b1601">問。祖師道。一念迴機。便同本得。迴機一句作麼生道。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b17"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711b1701" rend="margin-left:1em">答。更無一物&CB00453;尊堂。</p><p id="pX67p0711b1709" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。休云迦葉富。莫訝釋迦
<lb ed="X" n="0711b18"/>慳。月逐波沉海。雲隨鴈過山。不居生死宅。那住有
<lb ed="X" n="0711b19"/>無關。若昧迴機路。難逃作野犴。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b20"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711b2001">問。葉落歸根。來時無口。未審祖師那堭o這箇消息
<lb ed="X" n="0711b21"/>來。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711b2102" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。無言童子暗嗟吁。</p><p id="pX67p0711b2110" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。霜天雲際沒賓鴻。風
<lb ed="X" n="0711b22"/>捲平林萬樹空。向晚&CB00285;樓閑放目。難將有限&CB01904;無
<lb ed="X" n="0711b23"/>窮。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711b24"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711b2401">問。古人云。有道者得。無心者通。為甚麼道無心猶隔
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0711c" n="0711c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c01"/>一重關。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711c0104" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。彈指三下。</p><p id="pX67p0711c0109" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。&CB05169;泰興衰。情忘轉隔。得
<lb ed="X" n="0711c02"/>返紅衢。還迷紫陌。&CB00560;跟線斷了無拘。方信名為雲
<lb ed="X" n="0711c03"/>水客。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c04"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711c0401">問。古人道。修證則不無。染汙則不可。作麼生喚作染
<lb ed="X" n="0711c05"/>汙。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711c0502" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。含血噀人。</p><p id="pX67p0711c0507" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。萬里晴空。片雲點破。一翳不
<lb ed="X" n="0711c06"/>生。九鳥自墮。除去見聞覺知。併&CB00230;行住坐臥。&CB00457;清
<lb ed="X" n="0711c07"/>玉潔總如如。莫道精嚴無一箇。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711c0801">問。不用求真。唯須息見。祇如諸見如何息得。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711c0818" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。眼
<lb ed="X" n="0711c09"/>媯L筋一世貧。</p><p id="pX67p0711c0907" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。諸見息。平田未免生荊棘。荊棘
<lb ed="X" n="0711c10"/>林中得自由。方能透得黃金國。箇中真妄本無殊。
<lb ed="X" n="0711c11"/>為報禪人休費力。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711c1201">問。古人道。有一人常不喫飯不道飢。有一人終日喫
<lb ed="X" n="0711c13"/>飯不道飽。且道是一人。是二人。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711c1313" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。難兄難弟。</p><p id="pX67p0711c1318" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。
<lb ed="X" n="0711c14"/>飢不飢。飽不飽。無欠無餘非善巧。鼻孔昂藏模&CB01857;
<lb ed="X" n="0711c15"/>難。謾云<note n="0711002" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">壯疑狀</note>壯若雙垂瓜。是一人。是二人。屈指從頭數
<lb ed="X" n="0711c16"/>不真。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c17"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711c1701">問。得魚必假筌。得兔必假&CB04590;。不假筌&CB04590;。還得也無。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c18"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711c1801" rend="margin-left:1em">答。收來放去。</p><p id="pX67p0711c1806" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。恢恢天網&CB00520;非漏。水陸生靈難以
<lb ed="X" n="0711c19"/>透。點額華鯨更不移。桂宮白兔仍依舊。遇明時。當
<lb ed="X" n="0711c20"/>曉晝。呂尚從今莫下&CB00424;。成湯自此休秋狩。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c21"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0711c2101">問。德山棒如雨點。臨濟喝似雷奔。且道那箇最親切。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0711c22"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0711c2201" rend="margin-left:1em">答。南地竹兮北地木。</p><p id="pX67p0711c2209" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。拱密威嚴。全施號令。無
<lb ed="X" n="0711c23"/>劣無優。無偏無正。具眼兮針芥相投。擬心兮聖凡
<lb ed="X" n="0711c24"/>難並。當機棒喝沒人情。十聖三賢應乞命。</p></sp></dialog>
<pb ed="X" id="X67.1313.0712a" n="0712a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0712a01"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0712a0101">問。百尺竿頭須進步。十方世界現全身。且道百尺竿
<lb ed="X" n="0712a02"/>頭如何進步。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0712a0206" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。險。</p><p id="pX67p0712a0208" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。踢倒須彌。踏翻大地。左右
<lb ed="X" n="0712a03"/>逢源。縱橫無累。分身百億兮至化綿綿。撒手懸&CB00514;
<lb ed="X" n="0712a04"/>兮靈機異異。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0712a05"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0712a0501">問。情存向背。見處偏枯。且道仰山拂子是偏是正。</p></sp>
<lb ed="X" n="0712a06"/><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0712a0601" rend="margin-left:1em">答。信手拈來。</p><p id="pX67p0712a0606" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。玉線金針半夜穿。鼻微芒細巧相
<lb ed="X" n="0712a07"/>聯。從來妙用離情見。須信靈山有秘傳。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0712a08"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0712a0801">問。曹山云。諸方盡把格則語。何不與他道&CB00230;。且道如
<lb ed="X" n="0712a09"/>何為他道則是。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0712a0907" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。逢人不得錯舉。</p><p id="pX67p0712a0914" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。法不離心。
<lb ed="X" n="0712a10"/>波即是水。擬涉詮量。是非鋒起。古格分明舉似伊。
<lb ed="X" n="0712a11"/>桃紅李白薔薇紫。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0712a12"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0712a1201">問。龍牙云。待石烏龜解語即向汝道。且道那箇是石
<lb ed="X" n="0712a13"/>烏龜。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0712a1303" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。九宮八卦。</p><p id="pX67p0712a1308" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。石烏龜。分付汝。劈腹剜心
<lb ed="X" n="0712a14"/>無險阻。茫茫天下杜禪和。慎勿從今休錯舉。</p></sp></dialog>
<lb ed="X" n="0712a15"/><dialog type="qa"><sp type="question"><p id="pX67p0712a1501">問。德山云。我宗無語句。實無一法與人。且道德山還
<lb ed="X" n="0712a16"/>盡善也未。</p></sp><sp type="answer"><p id="pX67p0712a1605" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">答。駟不及舌。</p><p id="pX67p0712a1610" place="inline" rend="margin-left:1em">頌。雲出岫兮無心。月印
<lb ed="X" n="0712a17"/>江兮非意。直饒雲月如然。也是一場特地。舉身踏
<lb ed="X" n="0712a18"/>轉上頭關。應笑維摩垂不二。鷲嶺舉一花。少林開
<lb ed="X" n="0712a19"/>五葉。西乾布芬芳。東土光煒煠。五派各奔流。一言
<lb ed="X" n="0712a20"/>成勝捷。正偏能參差。祖代相承接。玉馬驟青霄。泥
<lb ed="X" n="0712a21"/>牛駕舟&CB00188;。蒼梧鳳不棲。古殿誰肯躡。撒手舊途中。
<lb ed="X" n="0712a22"/>主賓那交涉。&CB01366;肚飽&CB15763;&CB15763;。枕高安帖帖。綠水綠潺
<lb ed="X" n="0712a23"/>潺。青山青疊疊。</p></sp></dialog>
